{
  "id": "adv_main_02_07_01",
  "title": "東京編2章6話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、やるせないですね\n私達のことを守るためだからって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel so… helpless.\nThey did what they did to protect us….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "これじゃあまるで、トリエルの三人が身代わりになって\nプレタポルテへ移籍したみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is just like TRINITYAiLE sacrificed themselves for us\nby transferring over to Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "悔しいし、哀しいし……悔しいですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel bitter… and sad… and bitter‚ indeed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私達、瑠依さん達と仲間じゃなかったんですの？\n一緒にやっていこうって、約束したはずなのに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Weren’t we and TRINITYAiLE on the same team?\nI thought we promised to push through everything together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "連絡しても返事だってありませんし……\n何も出来ないまま、こんな急に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they’re not answering our calls.\nAnd they left so suddenly‚ leaving us powerless to do anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私も、すずちゃんと同じ気持ちだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same way as you‚ Suzu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何もしてあげられなかった、なんてことはないよ\nだからこそ、優ちゃん達は決断したんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we’re not powerless to do anything.\nThat’s the very reason why Yu-chan and the others made their decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "これ以上、仲間に迷惑は掛けたくないって……\nその優しさは、否定しないであげないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because they didn’t want to cause us any further pain.\nWe can’t reject their kindness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "分かっていますわ！　分かっていますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that! I understand it‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……こうなるとやっぱり\n三人はもう、星見プロには帰ってこない、のかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… with things as they are now‚\nwill the three of them never come back to Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "契約の内容次第ね\nどんな内容なのかまでは分からないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It depends on what their contract says.\nThough we still don’t know what’s in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、瑠依のお父さんの件もあるし\nそれが落ち着くまでは、派手な動きは出来ないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s still the scandal of Rui’s father.\nUntil that blows over‚ they can’t do anything too bold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "またすぐ移籍なんてしたら\nトリエルの印象が悪くなっちゃうから……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ if they transfer agencies right away again‚\nthat will tarnish TRINITYAiLE’s image… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあやっぱり\n今の私達がしてあげられることって、何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was right.\nThere’s nothing we can do to help them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 98
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないと思う\nきっと、出来ることはある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think that’s true.\nThere must be something we can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの会見だって、瑠依さん達は明らかに\n私達へ向けて言葉をくれてたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Take that press conference; Rui and the others were clearly\nsending us words of encouragement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "急な移籍で、確かに驚いたけど\nでも、ちゃんと心は繋がってるって思えたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sudden transfer did come as a shock‚\nbut I felt like our hearts were still connected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "事務所は関係なく\n他のアイドルと切磋琢磨して、より輝きたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn’t matter which agency we’re at.\n“By competing against the other idols‚ we want to shine even brighter.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなエールを受け取ったからには、応えないとね\nだからすずちゃん……もう泣かないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since they gave us that rallying call‚ we have to answer it.\nSo‚ Suzu-chan… stop crying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "な、泣いていませんわ！\nそれに、最初からそのつもりでしたのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but I am not crying!\nBesides‚ that was my intention from the very start!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの犠牲は、無駄になんかしません\nしっかり輝いて、目にものを見せてあげますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sacrifice of TRINITYAiLE will not have been in vain.\nWe will shine bright and show them what we’re made of!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.11774491071702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……身代わりっていうのはもののたとえだから\n本当に犠牲になった訳じゃない……よ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-um‚ the whole “sacrifice” thing was just a turn of phrase.\nThey didn’t literally sacrifice themselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、調子いいんだから\nでも、その意気や良し……ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are all overdramatic.\nBut I admire the resilience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、気持ち切り替えてレッスンしましょう\nトリエルからのエールに、応えるんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let’s shake it off with some lessons.\nYou want to answer TRINITYAiLE’s rallying call‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 163.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 163.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 163.93333333333337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1900.0000000000057,
          "startTime": 166.63333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 166.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら。どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura. What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 169.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "わっ\n……びっくりした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agh!\nYou scared me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 172.83333333333334
    },
    {
